 we also\nshow what could be done if some amount of non-linear information were included.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2012 04:21:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2012 10:18:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Mar 2012 15:23:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-02"}
